---
// Hero — Thomas Restrepo Portfolio
---

<section class="hero section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">

      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div class="hero-left">
        <p class="hero-location fade-up">Medellín, Colombia</p>

        <h1 class="hero-name fade-up delay-1">
          Thomas<br />Restrepo
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-title-label fade-up delay-2">Product Engineer</p>

        <p class="hero-pitch fade-up delay-3">
          Entiendo la lógica de tu negocio antes de escribir
          una línea de código. Diseño e implemento el sistema
          correcto — el que permite que tu negocio escale.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-ctas fade-up delay-4">
          <a href="mailto:thomasrr29@gmail.com" class="cta-primary">
            thomasrr29@gmail.com
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://linkedin.com/in/thomasrpo"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="cta-link"
          >LinkedIn</a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/Thomasrr29"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="cta-link"
          >GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: duotone photo -->
      <div class="hero-photo fade-up delay-3">
        <div class="photo-wrap">
          <img src="/yo.jpeg" alt="Thomas Restrepo" class="photo" />
          <div class="photo-overlay"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  /* ── Left ── */
  .hero-left {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* ── Location ── */
  .hero-location {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Name ── */
  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ── Title label ── */
  .hero-title-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  /* ── Pitch ── */
  .hero-pitch {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 48ch;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* ── CTAs ── */
  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-text);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-primary:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  .cta-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-link:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }

  /* ── Photo ── */
  .hero-photo {
    width: 280px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 360px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 15%;
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.1) brightness(0.95);
    transform: scale(1.65);
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  /* Duotone overlay: teal on top with multiply */
  .photo-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: #1D9E75;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    opacity: 0.55;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-photo {
      width: 200px;
    }

    .photo-wrap {
      width: 200px;
      height: 260px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-photo { display: none; }
  }
</style>
